===2020 census===
As of the [[census]] of 2020, it had a population of 2,519 inhabitants. 958 housing units.

===2010 census===
As of the [[census]] of 2010, it had a population of 2,507 inhabitants. 989 housing units. 1,213 are male. 1,294 are female.

